      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING DELORIS (1) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts two wins and three placings. Scored by 2.75 lengths last time (19.91) in a Grade 5 over 340m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. BLAINE KEEPING (3) boasts a strong record this journey with 20 wins and 13 minors from 41 tries. Placed last time (19.92) at this track in a Free For All, finishing second and beaten 5.5 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. COOKIE MAN (2) finished well back at Maitland last time when a 9 length fifth (22.68) but recorded best time of the card when winning five back. Solid record here at the distance winning six races. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Likely to be about the money. SHORTY BOY (7) missed the frame latest (22.85) when eighth over 400m at Maitland in a NG. Has already won four times from this draw.",
